<view class="detail-page">
  <view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="detail-body">
    <view class="section-card detail-summary">
      <view class="section-title">房源详情加载中</view>
      <view class="detail-copy">正在从后端读取当前房源信息。</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:elif="{{loadFailed}}" class="detail-body">
    <view class="section-card detail-summary">
      <view class="section-title">房源详情加载失败</view>
      <view class="detail-copy">当前详情页会临时通过 `/api/v1/house/search` 结果兜底查找房源。若失败，请检查房源 ID 是否仍能在公开搜索结果中查到。</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <block wx:else>
    <swiper wx:if="{{gallery.length > 0}}" class="gallery-swiper" circular indicator-dots autoplay>
      <swiper-item wx:for="{{gallery}}" wx:key="*this">
        <image class="gallery-image" src="{{item}}" mode="aspectFill" />
      </swiper-item>
    </swiper>
    <view wx:else class="gallery-placeholder"></view>

    <view class="detail-body">
      <view class="section-card detail-summary">
        <view class="detail-price-row">
          <view>
            <text class="price">{{priceText}}</text>
            <text class="price-unit">月租</text>
          </view>
          <text class="tiny">当前通过公开搜索结果临时兜底展示</text>
        </view>
        <view class="detail-title">{{title}}</view>
        <view class="feature-grid">
          <view wx:for="{{features}}" wx:key="label" class="feature-item">
            <text class="feature-label">{{item.label}}</text>
            <text class="feature-value">{{item.value}}</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="section-card detail-ai-card">
        <view class="section-title">说明</view>
        <view class="detail-copy">当前公开房源详情接口还没补齐，这里先通过公开搜索结果做临时详情展示。</view>
        <view class="detail-copy">后续后端补上正式的 `/api/v1/house/detail` 后，这里会直接切回真正的详情请求。</view>
      </view>

      <view class="section-card detail-tag-card">
        <view class="section-title">房源标签</view>
        <view class="tag-row">
          <text wx:for="{{tags}}" wx:key="*this" class="house-tag">{{item}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="section-card detail-info-card">
        <view class="section-title">详细信息</view>
        <view wx:for="{{infoItems}}" wx:key="label" class="info-row">
          <text class="info-label">{{item.label}}</text>
          <text class="info-value">{{item.value}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="section-card detail-advisor-card">
        <view>
          <view class="section-title">下一步建议</view>
          <view class="detail-copy">如果你要继续做租客端体验，下一步最需要后端补的是公开房源列表和公开房源详情接口。</view>
        </view>
        <button class="btn-ghost">继续联调</button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </block>
</view>
